dct_title_s: Carta geológica da República da Guiné-Bissau  / coordinação  par Paulo Hagendorn Alves ; interpretação geológica par Heitor de Carlvalho ; Laboratório Nacional de Energia e Geologia (LNEG).
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by countours, spot heights, and gradient tints. Depth shown by soundings. On recto: cross section., table of mineral occurrences . On verso:Meso-Cenozoic basin cross section, litostratographic logs, notes, and index to topographic maps, scale 1:50,000.
dct_creator_sm: Guinea-Bissau. Direction de la géologie et des mines
dct_publisher_sm: Lisboa : Direcção Geral de Geologia e Minas, 2011.
